TextEng: What do you charge for a room?
What pay for room?
May I ask you some questions?
Me questions ask you?
Goodbye.
That'll do.
You no make fun or arms get ripped off!
Save stupid jokes and tell what me pay.
Text: 바보 같은 농담 집어치우고 얼마 내야 하는지 말해.

TextEng: Has there been anything odd going on around here?
Do you know where I might find some work in town?
Text: 마을에서 일자리를 어디서 구할 수 있는지 알아?

TextEng: Perhaps you could give me some directions?
Where me get job?
Bad stuff happen 'round here?
Nevermind.
What do you know about the plague?
But the plague is over, why dwell on the past?
Text: 하지만 역병은 끝났잖아, 왜 과거에 매달리는 거야?

TextEng: Werewolves? Where did you hear about werewolves?
Well, that doesn't interest me. Can I ask you some other questions?
Text: 글쎄, 그건 관심 없어. 다른 질문해도 돼?

TextEng: Nature? What do you mean?
What a wonderful little theory. Why don't we get back to something a little more interesting?
Text: 참 훌륭한 이론이네. 좀 더 재밌는 얘기로 돌아가지 않을래?

TextEng: Well, I suppose I will go talk to Ander then. Goodbye.
Text: 그럼 앤더랑 얘기하러 가야겠다. 잘 있어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Is there anyone else I should talk to about the werewolves?
Text: <StartCheck>[직관]</Start> 늑대인간에 대해 얘기해야 할 다른 사람이 있어?

TextEng: Maybe I should talk to him, but first could you answer another question?
Text: 그 사람과 얘기해야 할 것 같긴 한데, 먼저 다른 질문 하나 대답해줄래?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> What? You can tell me. I won't repeat anything, I swear.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 뭔데? 말해봐. 아무에게도 안 말할게, 맹세해.

TextEng: I guess I'll go talk to them.
I suspect you are overly paranoid. I'd better talk to Alhelor now.
Text: 너무 편집증적인 것 같아. 이제 알헬러랑 얘기해봐야겠다.

TextEng: That's interesting. Maybe I could ask you a few more questions?
Text: 흥미롭네. 몇 가지 더 물어봐도 될까?

TextEng: Whatever. Maybe you could answer a few more questions though?
Text: 뭐든. 몇 가지 더 대답해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Where can I find some supplies?
This place is called Port Llast. I assume that means there are docks around here somewhere.
Text: 여긴 라스트 항구라고 불리잖아. 그럼 어딘가에 부두가 있겠지.

TextEng: What do you mean by that?
All right. I have a few more questions for you.
Text: 알았어. 몇 가지 더 질문이 있어.

TextEng: Goodbye.
I don't suppose so. Could you answer another question?
Text: 그런 것 같진 않아. 다른 질문에 대답해줄래?

TextEng: Okay, maybe you could answer another question?
Okay. Goodbye.
All right, I will do that. Goodbye.
Okay, but first I would like to ask you another question.
Text: 알았어, 하지만 먼저 다른 질문 하나 할게.

TextEng: I will do that. Goodbye.
I might, but first I have another question.
Text: 그럴 수도 있는데, 먼저 다른 질문이 있어.

TextEng: That sounds good. See you later.
Maybe, but first another question.
Text: 그럴 수도, 근데 먼저 다른 질문.

TextEng: Where werewolf?
Crazy trees?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Who else knows werewolf?
Okay, me go talk Ander now.
Text: 알았어, 나 이제 앤더한테 가서 얘기해.

TextEng: Me want more questions.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> What me no nevermind?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 신경 안 써도 되는 거 뭐야?

TextEng: Me be okay. Me be tough customer. Bye.
Text: 나 괜찮아. 나 강해. 잘 있어.

TextEng: Me no worry. Me have more questions.
Text: 나 걱정 안 해. 질문 더 있어.

TextEng: Me done here. Bye.
Me want more questions.
Ballard. A duck?
Okay, but first you answer more questions.
Text: 알았어, 근데 먼저 질문 더 대답해.

TextEng: Okay, me go find Ballard.
Oh, okay. Now you answer another question.
Text: 아, 알았어. 이제 다른 질문 대답해.

TextEng: You help me find places?
That's all I need thank you.
Could you answer another question?
Where me get good stuff?
Why this place called Port Llast? You have docks here?
Text: 왜 여기 라스트 항구라고 불러? 여기 부두 있어?

TextEng: Okay, me go.
Now you answer more questions.
Why not be safe?
Me have more questions.
Me not scared of werewolf! Now answer new question.
Text: 나 늑대인간 안 무서워! 이제 새 질문 대답해.

TextEng: Maybe, but me want ask 'nother question.
Text: 그럴 수도, 근데 나 다른 질문 할래.

TextEng: Me do that. Bye bye.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Me need get money for new tax from you.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 나 너한테 새 세금 받으러 왔어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> I'm here to collect the new tavern tax.
<StartAction>[Lie]</Start> You pay, or me close you place down. Aribeth and Nasher say so.
Text: <StartAction>[거짓말]</Start> 돈 내, 아니면 가게 문 닫아. 아리베스랑 나셰르가 그랬어.

TextEng: Ha! Me fool you good.
<StartAction>[Lie]</Start> You'll pay, or this tavern will be shut down on the orders of Lady Aribeth and Lord Nasher.
Text: <StartAction>[거짓말]</Start> 돈 내, 아니면 아리베스 여사와 나셰르 영주의 명으로 이 술집을 폐쇄할 거야.

TextEng: Calm down man, it was only a joke.
